{"serial": "53023", "department_serial": 52, "code": "CO6060", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Internet of Things Technology", "ch": "物聯網技術"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": "與SG5007合班授課。"}, "instructor": {"en": ["Hu, Chih-Lin", "Wu, Jung-Shyr"], "ch": ["胡誌麟", "吳中實"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 1, "session": ["5", "6", "7"]}, "loc": {"building": "E1", "room": "219"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 25, "department": {"ch": "通訊工程學系", "en": "Department of Communication Engineering"}, "system": {"ch": "碩博同修", "en": "Master/Doctoral Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "部分英語", "en": "Partially English"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 7, "selected": 24, "remark": {"ch": "與SG5007合班授課。", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程目標是培訓學生了解物聯網核心技術中的底層感測及區域網路技術；物聯網中層核心網路技術；上層服務平台技術及相關國際標準，並且搭配實驗實習課程培養學生在物聯網實務上的開發能力。課程進程將是透過一系列實作技術課程，讓學生熟悉操作物聯網開發裝置、進而將理論應用在實際場域內，且導入Problem-Based Learning (PBL) 教學方式訓練學生自主學習。本課程後段，將導入PBL問題導向的教學方式，透過生活中實際問題及情境，引導學生聚焦於特定且真實的問題、思索和採取合宜的解決方法。學生藉由小組討論，於期末專題競賽時，展現團隊合作的成果。透過此教學方式來增強學生的創造力與實踐力。修習完本課程的學生將具備物聯網架構及相關技術之知識、在物聯網裝置上開發物聯網應用之能力及PBL教學方式所帶給學生之自主學習力。", "en": "The objective of course is to teach students to learn the technology of basic sensor and personal area networks, core network, upper layer service platform and related international standard with lab courses of implementation. The students will get the knowledge of\nInternet of Things (IoT) technology and application implementation in the IoT devices. \nThe goal of this course is to train students to understand the underlying sensing and local network technology in the core technologies of the Internet of Things; the middle-level core network technology of the Internet of Things; the upper-level service platform technology and related international standards, and to train students in the practice of the Internet of Things application development abilities. The course process will be through a series of practical technical courses to familiarize students with operating IoT devices, and then apply the theory to the actual field. In the latter part of this course, the students will be introduced by the Problem-Based Learning (PBL) process to train themselves to learn independently. PBL methods will be introduced to guide students to focus on specific and real problems, think and adopt appropriate solutions through actual problems and situations in life. Students in groups will do teamwork for the final project. Through this PBL method, students‘ creativity and practical ability are enhanced. Students who have completed this course will have knowledge of the Internet of Things architecture and related technologies, the ability to develop Internet of Things applications, and the self-learning ability that the PBL methods bring to students."}, "outline": {"ch": "週次內容備註\n1物聯網發展現況與前瞻\n2物聯網系統架構\n3物聯網通訊網路技術\n4無線通訊網路、感測網路及隨意網路簡介\n5行動及無線異質網路簡介\n6物聯網平台與感測裝置之通訊整合實驗一\n7物聯網平台與感測裝置之通訊整合\n8物聯網網路安全實驗二\n9期中考\n10物聯網平台架設軟體定義網路閘道器之拓樸控制\n11物聯網平台與多重路徑資料流之軟體定義網路\n12物聯網平台與終端裝置之頻寬調節實驗三\n13PBL學習-問題情境的發想與設計(物聯網平台與智慧居家)\n14PBL學習-設計思維(物聯網平台與居家照護)\n實驗四\n15PBL學習-引導專題發想與問題反思(物聯網平台與網路安全)實驗五\n16PBL學習-專題製作一\n17PBL學習-專題製作二\n18期末專期展示及報告", "en": "週次內容備註\n1IoT Technology: An Introduction and Overview\n2IoT System Architecture\n3IoT Communication Technologies\n4Wireless, Sensor and Ad Hoc Networks for IoT\n5Mobile Networks or IoT\n6IoT Service SDK and Sensor Module IntegrationExperiment 1\n7IoT Service SDK and Sensor Module Integration\n8IoT and Network SecurityExperiment 2\n9Midterm Exam\n10IoT SDN Gateway and Topology Control\n11IoT SDN Gateway and Data Flow Control\n12IoT and Network Bandwidth Allocation for End DevicesExperiment 3\n13PBL Project Scenario and Design (Smart Home)Experiment 4\n14PBL Project Design Thinking (Home Care)\n15PBL Project Ideation and Problem Reflection (Network Security)Experiment 5\n16PBL Project Prototypical Implementation\n17PBL Project Prototypical Implementation\n18Final Project and Presentation"}, "textbook": {"ch": "原有課程教材(1/3)；「物聯網核心技術及應用專題課程模組」之教材(1/3)；\n新編嵌入式物聯網應用教材(1/3)", "en": "原有課程教材(1/3)；「物聯網核心技術及應用專題課程模組」之教材(1/3)；\n新編嵌入式物聯網應用教材(1/3)"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "99", "en": "99"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n\n實習/實驗\n\n其他", "en": ["Lecture", "", "Practical Training Lab", "", "Others"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "•期中考(Mid-term Exam) 30  ％\n•期末專題(Final Project) 30  ％\n•實驗作業 (Homework) 40  ％", "en": "•期中考(Mid-term Exam) 30  ％\n•期末專題(Final Project) 30  ％\n•實驗作業 (Homework) 40  ％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "胡誌麟週一 11:00-11:50；週二 14:00-14:50。吳中實週四、週五12:00-12:50", "en": "Hu Mon. 11:00-11:50；Tue 14:00-14:50。Wu Thu.,Fri. 12:00-12:50"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "通訊網路", "en": "通訊網路"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "工程專業知識運用", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "實驗設計與數據解析", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "工程實作及專業語文", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "工程系統設計", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "團隊合作", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "問題分析及獨立解決", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "國際視野與終身學習", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "社會責任", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["出席/課堂表現"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Applying Engineering Specialism", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Practices/Experiments"]}, {"competencies": "Experiment Design and Data Analysis", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Practices/Experiments"]}, {"competencies": "Engineering Practice and Professional Presentation", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Engineering System Design", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Practices/Experiments"]}, {"competencies": "Team Work", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Practices/Experiments", "Attendance/Performance"]